528
00:40:31,360 --> 00:40:33,980
[SPEAKER_00] potreću empatije, intimnosti,

529
00:40:33,980 --> 00:40:36,860
[SPEAKER_00] socijalnih odnosa

530
00:40:36,860 --> 00:40:38,940
[SPEAKER_00] i samodirektivnost, identiteta.

531
00:40:38,940 --> 00:40:42,719
[SPEAKER_00] Znam ko sam i ostvarujem neke rezultate.

532
00:40:42,719 --> 00:40:43,780
[SPEAKER_00] Super.

533
00:40:43,780 --> 00:40:45,239
[SPEAKER_00] Dok je gotovo ide,

534
00:40:45,239 --> 00:40:46,639
[SPEAKER_00] to je poanta svega.

535
00:40:46,639 --> 00:40:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] Da to transformiraš

536
