537
00:40:50,219 --> 00:40:51,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ako pak ne možeš,

538
00:40:51,980 --> 00:40:53,139
[SPEAKER_00] trajiš opciju BCD,

539
00:40:53,139 --> 00:40:54,940
