540
00:40:55,719 --> 00:40:56,900
[SPEAKER_00] Meni neki ljudi kažu

541
00:40:56,900 --> 00:40:58,619
[SPEAKER_00] oni to ne mogu pa šmrću kokain.

542
00:40:58,619 --> 00:41:00,420
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, je to rješenje

543
00:41:00,420 --> 00:41:02,559
[SPEAKER_00] ili neki prošvikaju

544
00:41:02,559 --> 00:41:03,760
[SPEAKER_00] ili odustane od svega.

545
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:05,480
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ima opcija, ono,

546
00:41:05,480 --> 00:41:06,719
[SPEAKER_00] i Bog će ti dati.

547
00:41:06,719 --> 00:41:07,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ako vjeruješ da će ti,

548
00:41:07,719 --> 00:41:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] će biti otvoren

549
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] ko švedski stol

550
00:41:11,960 --> 00:41:13,760
