554
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:18,880
[SPEAKER_00] Bitno je pobjediti, da to.

555
00:41:18,880 --> 00:41:20,139
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je bitno pobjediti.

556
00:41:20,139 --> 00:41:21,139
[SPEAKER_01] Meni isto bitno pobjediti.

557
00:41:21,139 --> 00:41:22,440
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je dao kad je neka frka,

558
00:41:22,440 --> 00:41:23,039
[SPEAKER_01] ali nešto.

559
00:41:24,960 --> 00:41:26,360
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo je naš duhovnik

560
00:41:26,360 --> 00:41:27,340
[SPEAKER_01] fra Ivan Marija Lota

561
