[SPEAKER_01] toliko i toliko puta,

566
00:41:35,039 --> 00:41:37,659
[SPEAKER_01] onako treba nogon udari i to.

567
00:41:37,659 --> 00:41:40,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ali isto tako je našta,

568
00:41:40,400 --> 00:41:43,219
[SPEAKER_01] nekako kao da mi Isus kaže

569
