575
00:41:54,199 --> 00:41:55,199
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kreni.

576
00:41:55,199 --> 00:41:57,019
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, pomaže da, ono,

577
00:41:57,019 --> 00:41:59,019
