581
00:42:04,699 --> 00:42:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] slušaje negdje i u nekom mjestu

582
00:42:06,599 --> 00:42:08,739
[SPEAKER_00] i bude realan.

583
00:42:08,739 --> 00:42:11,659
[SPEAKER_00] I naravno da krene i testira

584
00:42:11,659 --> 00:42:13,980
[SPEAKER_00] i vidi jel ide

585
00:42:13,980 --> 00:42:16,139
[SPEAKER_00] i pokuša i pokuša i pokuša.

586
00:42:16,139 --> 00:42:17,320
[SPEAKER_00] Samo treba biti realan

587
00:42:17,320 --> 00:42:18,739
[SPEAKER_00] oko sebe

588
00:42:18,739 --> 00:42:19,719
[SPEAKER_00] i zazivat

589
00:42:19,719 --> 00:42:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] ok,

590
00:42:20,960 --> 00:42:23,679
[SPEAKER_00] reko, život ima smisla,

591
00:42:23,679 --> 00:42:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj trenutak je dio života,

592
00:42:26,539 --> 00:42:27,579
