593
00:42:27,579 --> 00:42:29,099
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj trenutak ima smisla.

594
00:42:29,099 --> 00:42:30,860
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo u ovom trenutku sada

595
00:42:30,860 --> 00:42:32,760
[SPEAKER_00] meni dolazi taj naš

596
00:42:32,760 --> 00:42:34,559
[SPEAKER_00] super bog

597
00:42:34,559 --> 00:42:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] koji je dobar

598
00:42:35,380 --> 00:42:37,559
[SPEAKER_00] i daje mi snagu i sve.

599
00:42:37,559 --> 00:42:38,260
[SPEAKER_00] I opet,

600
00:42:38,260 --> 00:42:40,019
[SPEAKER_00] možeš uz to

601
00:42:40,019 --> 00:42:42,119
[SPEAKER_00] imat granulom.

602
00:42:42,119 --> 00:42:43,579
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš imat zubobolju

