00:42:47,500 --> 00:42:47,940
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

608
00:42:47,940 --> 00:42:50,280
[SPEAKER_00] samo da ne moram to.

609
00:42:50,280 --> 00:42:51,639
[SPEAKER_00] A možeš imat u tom trenutku

610
00:42:51,639 --> 00:42:52,300
[SPEAKER_00] temperaturu.

611
00:42:52,300 --> 00:42:53,900
